Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼要哭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.79,0:00:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.06,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看起來豈不像是我在單方面地欺負後輩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭的是我才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.50,0:00:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但被妹妹敬而遠之 而且連個理由都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼不對我訴說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說我就只是這種程度的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 成為姐妹又有甚麼意義呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼你要接受念珠呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另找一天心平氣和地再談談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也稍微有點過於激動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.61,0:01:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能說得也太過份了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.01,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始商議明天活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.27,0:01:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.17,0:01:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也想單方面地將我當成壞人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.75,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.09,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.71,0:01:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.08,0:01:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.57,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒緩的行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃驚的巧克力·後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是四季常開呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概被姐姐討厭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想你或許願意自已一個人待著 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說起來 剛才真像是過去情景的重現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳與祥子有時真是相似得讓人吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.00,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的祐巳與祥子\N就像是一年又十個月以前的祥子與蓉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是現在的紅薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.41,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子因為成長環境的原因 所以不大擅長表達自已的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常因悶得慌而發脾氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祥子大人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子對她訓斥道「你這樣我甚麼都無法明白」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有想說的話就清楚地說出來」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼不說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你內心深處的話語為甚麼就不能向我傾訴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話我甚麼都無法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被蓉子那樣訓斥後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子也像是忍耐到了極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後就漸漸變得能表達自已的意見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這大概就是祥子對祐巳感到焦躁不安的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦躁不安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為看到祐巳就像是看到了自已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子她的本性並未改變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才焦躁不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.27,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在祐巳的身上\N看到了自已身上也有的討厭部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以原諒祥子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒甚麼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 不要因為這點事就變得討厭祥子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對這個溫室 稍微有點過敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人很快就要畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再沒有能像這樣來幫助我的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是說了些讓人開心的話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能再多向祥子訴說一些真心話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衹要至少能做到一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管發生甚麼事一定都能順利地渡過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 向祐巳佈置一道作業題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑自已的力量與祥子重歸於好 好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～ 祐巳不送我巧克力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.24,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向志摩子同學說聲「給我巧克力」不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼只有放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.96,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給我巧克力的話 我就吃掉祐巳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊是祥子大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.47,0:07:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗品就留作用情不專的白薔薇大人的懲罰用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先必須對昨天的事道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 將祥子大人叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祐巳同學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同學也許把卡片藏在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再胡鬧了 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告訴我卡片藏在哪裡也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只聽一下我的預測好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.93,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能否把這個吵人傢伙帶出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是小氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學 請稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 昨天真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.99,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 如果方便的話 今天能給我一點時間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想繼續昨天的話題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋寶結束後如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我在溫室等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那麼就在溫室見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝大家的勇躍參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.63,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我說明一下活動規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要找的就是這些卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅 白 黃的卡片將分別藏在校內的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制時間是一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到卡片後 請帶回到作為本部的薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.18,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著就可獲贈\N作為附加獎的與花蕾們的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請花蕾的姐妹們到前面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了公平起見 請花蕾的姐妹們遲五分鐘開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！ 怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在活動結束前 花蕾們請來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到黃薔薇大人竟然也會參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒理由白白放過這麼有趣的活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我一定會找到紅色的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 稍微招呼一下客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 方便的話能否進來談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有花蕾們在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.66,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人不想去找志摩子同學的卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你說是志摩子的卡片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 關於隱藏的地點我是一點頭緒也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 明明志摩子同學的卡片大概就在那裡的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說那個房間裡藏著甚麼好東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 已過了5分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待著祐巳的英勇奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.31,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊 志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟白薔薇大人約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人既沒參加甚麼俱樂部活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒加入甚麼委員會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是在薔薇館裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是祥子大人的FAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概以為我知道卡片藏在哪裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.14,0:12:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～ 現在可不是玩捉迷藏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 還有十五分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人的紅色卡片到底在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我要藏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的話 一定會藏在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 好像嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是來這裡找卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人 比我更早來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 看起來還未找到卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.35,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想卡片應該就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話 請用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那裡沒有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.11,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我說晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上我剛才也挖掘過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼會認為卡片在那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.43,0:14:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個薔薇就叫做紅薔薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到4點40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加活動的同學們請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 我們將發表本次活動的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾們的卡片有兩張被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 沒找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為令不給我提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為一定會在那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是找到白色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年級藤組 蟹名靜同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～ 是靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明用表情給過提示的 這個人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到白色卡片的地點是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委員會的公告牌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 不在薔薇館的第一層嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼志摩子同學為甚麼那時會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 是找到黃色卡片的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級菊組 田沼千里同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點是在圖書館裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖書館我也去找過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅薔薇的花蕾的卡片誰也沒發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅薔薇的花蕾 紅色卡片究竟在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 一起去收回卡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 卻沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找了哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在紅薔薇根莖的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的找了這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明挖掘過同一個地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學 雖然很遺憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有證人在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.35,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是… 不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就沒法成為證人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都說到這種地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.42,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 這張卡片放在了比我原來埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖瓦倫丁做了一個惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣去想不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然紅薔薇的花蕾都這樣說了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 能在薔薇館等我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.07,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.12,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.41,0:17:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特意等在這裡為你送的巧克力說聲謝謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力的話這裡有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是非常難吃的夾心巧克力就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 放在那裡的巧克力不是祐巳的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.18,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 我已經吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.20,0:18:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為祐巳緊盯著那扇門 所以我完全以為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常美味的大理石花紋蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.06,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像是初學者做的 樣子稍微有點變形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那是粉紅色的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 粉紅色的包裝紙上印著白色薔薇花紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.15,0:18:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薔薇館第一層裡藏的不是白色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.65,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是志摩子同學因為猶豫著該不該交給\N白薔薇大人而一直放在那裡的巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算聖瓦倫丁的一個惡作劇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有東西希望你能收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道… 不會是念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念珠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我一年級的時候 好像是被姐姐完全看穿了似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.52,0:19:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我對你的心事卻不怎麼了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以漸漸變得沒有自信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 看起來你好像在避開我 所以稍微有點急躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那是我的誤解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.27,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那是因為我想把這個送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在令大人的幫助下做出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為想先對姐姐保密 才會偷偷摸摸地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人在那裡沾沾自喜地做得起勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻完全沒有想到姐姐會怎麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.93,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的 姐姐討厭情人節的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我無論如何也想將\N平常那種感謝的心情化為有形的物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.35,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過討厭甚麼的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所厭煩的只是一部份學生隨便地\N將送巧克力的慾望想放在我身上實現而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.31,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你為我做的東西的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會很高興地收下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能給我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了我不是討厭巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一個不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 請拿這邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人請放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.64,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳你才應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 又是在做甚麼表演嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.76,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的 這叫做「吃驚的巧克力」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.82,0:21:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面混入了難吃得讓人歪嘴的「不中」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才叫「吃驚」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.94,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那就是「中」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明「中」與「不中」都有一個不見了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人會吃到「中」也算是聖瓦倫丁的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.67,0:21:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到「中」會有甚麼好事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到「中」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.49,0:22:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會無一例外地獲贈與我的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.87,0:23:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被不認識的某人偷偷地思念也是很浪漫的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到是喜歡清清楚楚、明明白白地去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想下一周的故事一定會讓人焦躁不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也會一邊發牢騷一邊看下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.45,0:23:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話一點都不像姐姐 只是一個老姑婆而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.00,0:23:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
